snippet.title: Those Who Remain - Announcement trailer
snippet.description:
Edward Turner is just an ordinary man with a troubled past, who arrives in the wrong place at the wrong time. 
He will soon find out that something is very wrong in Dormont.

More info on: http://www.thosewhoremain.com 
Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/715380
